  "title": "Technical Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supporting the vessel manager in purchasing spare parts &amp; consumables for ships</li>\n  <li>Responsible for document control (e.g. maintain check list of periodic reporting due      from vessel)</li>\n  <li>Keeping record of the technical operating costs, Verification of Invoices and DAs</li>\n  <li>Arranging and coordinating logistics for supplies and service arrangements for ship</li>\n  <li>Maintain up to date records of all the vessels Certificates, manuals, drawings      &amp; instruction books</li>\n  <li>Assist in arranging routine vessel repairs</li>\n  <li>Assisting vessel manager with daily operations of the vessels</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2 -  3 years of working experience in a ship management, ship owning      company or purchase department with vessel international voyages.</li>\n  <li>Proficient in Microsoft Office applications.</li>\n  <li>Responsible, Meticulous and able to work under pressure</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of ShipNet / Eyeshare software system will be an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Chan Chee Meng</p>\n<p>EA 07C3069</p>\n<p>R1110620</p>",
